ГўВҖВңThe Secretary of Health;

ГўВҖВңThe Secretary of Labor and Employment or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe Secretary of the Interior and Local Government or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe Secretary of Social Welfare and Development or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe Secretary of the Department of Finance (DOF) or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe President and Chief Executive Officer (CEO) of the Corporation;

ГўВҖВңThe SSS Administrator or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe GSIS General Manager or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe Vice Chairperson for the basic sector of the National Anti-Poverty Commission or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңThe Chairperson of the Civil Service Commission (CSC) or a permanent representative;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of Filipino migrant workers;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of the members in the informal economy;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of Filipino migrant workers;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of the members in the informal economy;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of the members in the formal economy;

ГўВҖВңA representative of employers;

ГўВҖВңA representative of health care providers to be endorsed by their national associations of health care institutions and medical health professionals;

ГўВҖВңA permanent representative of the elected local chief executives to be endorsed by the League of Provinces, League of Cities and League of Municipalities; and

